The paper deals with the capacity of a communication system, specifically a massive MIMO system, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The use of 1-bit ADCs and DACs is a common technique in signal processing (cs.SI) and networking (cs.NI) to reduce hardware complexity and power consumption. Finally, the use of multiple antennas is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) for improving wireless communication performance.
